<h5 id="get-accesstokenrequest">GET /accesstokenrequest</h5>
<hr />
<ul>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">controllers/accesstokenrequest.js</code>ì—ì„œëŠ” authorization headerì— ë‹´ê¸´ í† í°ì´ ì„œë²„ì—ì„œ ìƒì„±í•œ JWTì¸ì§€ í™•ì¸í›„, ì„œë²„ì—ì„œ ìƒì„±í•œ ìœ íš¨í•œ í† í°ì¼ ê²½ìš°ì™€ ìœ íš¨í•˜ì§€ ì•Šì€ í† í°ì¼ ê²½ìš° ê°ê° ë‹¤ë¥¸ ì‘ë‹µì„ ë°˜í™˜ í•´ì•¼í•œë‹¤.</p>

    <div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">authorization</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">req</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">headers</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">authorization</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">];</span>  <span class="c1">// authorization headerì— ë‹´ê¸´ í† í°ì„ ë³€ìˆ˜ì— ì €ì¥</span>

